WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.377 --> 00:00:01.268
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.268 --> 00:00:02.159
Praise the Lord!

00:00:02.159 --> 00:00:04.266
Thank you for joining me today.

00:00:04.617 --> 00:00:16.864
I got a text message from Sister Billy Brim, and she had somebody reach out to her from Australia who is pretty well known.

00:00:17.260 --> 00:00:29.537
This person had a dream, and in the dream, she told Billy that the dream was about Trump.

00:00:29.955 --> 00:00:42.768
Trump was at some kind of rally at a hockey rink, and he was fatally shot from the audience, and it was live on TV.

00:00:44.520 --> 00:00:58.219
She didn't know that he was going to do this rally in the next couple of days in Washington, so she looked up to see if he was doing anything, basically trying to figure out anything she could about the dream she had.

00:00:58.599 --> 00:01:09.394
She found out that the rally he's going to have on the 19th is at a hockey and basketball stadium.

00:01:10.143 --> 00:01:28.679
It's very alarming when another fellow watchman is seeing another warning, warning the people to pray that there is going to be an attempt on President Trump's life on the 19th, which is what they're thinking.

00:01:29.079 --> 00:01:40.146
Sister Billy asked me to have you all pray and intercede for President Trump for protection for his wife, for his kids, all of it.

00:01:41.639 --> 00:01:44.988
The enemy knows, folks, what's about to happen.

00:01:44.988 --> 00:02:04.489
He knows that his days are numbered, and he is trying to throw his last and final blows as much as he can to kill, steal, and destroy, trying to derail God's plan for this earth for one last call.

00:02:04.834 --> 00:02:14.400
I'm telling you all, Trump plays a big part in what's about to take place, and the enemy knows it.

00:02:16.200 --> 00:02:17.325
He knows; he's heard all the prophetic words.

00:02:19.080 --> 00:02:27.620
He knows what's being said in the spirit realm, so if he can try to derail that, he thinks he's winning.

00:02:31.507 --> 00:02:34.800
But we know we have power and authority over the devil, and nothing shall by any means hurt us.

00:02:34.800 --> 00:02:45.120
But we have to take our authority; we have to take our seat and our place, and we have to do it daily.

00:02:45.120 --> 00:02:55.274
We're seated with Him in the heavenlies, far above all principalities and powers and might according to Ephesians.

00:03:05.405 --> 00:03:05.788
Read the book of Ephesians over and over until it becomes real to you.

00:03:05.788 --> 00:03:09.119
It's my favorite book, that and Hebrews.

00:03:09.119 --> 00:03:10.560
I love Hebrews.

00:03:16.698 --> 00:03:17.053
I love the books that just stir you up, and I would encourage you all to read Ephesians.

00:03:17.409 --> 00:03:28.140
I take it very seriously when Sister Billy would ask for something like this because she's never done this before, and so I trust her discernment.

00:03:37.533 --> 00:03:37.817
I trust the way she prays; she has imparted so much.

00:03:37.817 --> 00:03:42.593
I'm telling you all, if she's taking it seriously, we need to take it seriously.

00:03:42.593 --> 00:03:53.840
This is something that has really stirred in her to call and say, 'Hey, listen, we need to have a prayer army over this.

00:03:53.840 --> 00:03:58.048
' So I really want you all to take this time right now.

00:03:58.048 --> 00:04:00.100
We're going to pray for President Trump.

00:04:00.100 --> 00:04:11.580
