00:04:36.400 --> 00:04:42.000
It could have been a lot worse, of course, as we all know.

00:04:42.000 --> 00:04:46.570
But this time, nothing is going to happen.

00:04:46.570 --> 00:04:47.873
Do you see?

00:04:47.873 --> 00:04:56.005
Because now we're going to bring up a prayer army, and this is what we're called to do.

00:05:09.971 --> 00:05:10.280
